TO GENERATE THIS PDF:
1. Open printables/evacuation-kit.html in Chrome
2. File → Print
3. Destination: Save as PDF
4. Layout: Portrait. Margins: Default. Headers and footers: ON
5. Save as: printables/evacuation-kit.pdf
6. Delete this .todo file
7. git add printables/evacuation-kit.html printables/evacuation-kit.pdf
8. git rm printables/evacuation-kit.pdf.todo
9. git commit -m "chore: generate evacuation kit PDF"
